events.text:
The marshlands is a teeming ecosystem full of marvelous wonder, at times creating its very own life.
This life has been rather hostile recently for reasons I'm not sure of.
Go to the fungal forest west of here to investigate anything strange that might be causing this hostility.
Did you find anything strange in the forest?
Just as I feared, the corruption has already spreaded and driven the spores mad. Hmmm...
